        {
            "id": "https://scriptlink.rarelysimple.com/blog/announcing-avatarscriptlink.net-1.1.10/",
            "content_html": "<p>AvatarScriptLink.NET version 1.1.10 is <a href=\"https://www.nuget.org/packages/RarelySimple.AvatarScriptLink/1.1.10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"\">now available on NuGet</a>.</p>\n<!-- -->\n<p>This release corrects <a href=\"https://github.com/rarelysimple/RarelySimple.AvatarScriptLink/issues/22\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"\">a reported issue causing some using the OpenForm Error Code (6) to fail</a>.</p>",
